\section{Application to G\lowercase{a}$_2$O$_3$}

After the proposal of a rather general categorization of biaxial crystals and analytical formulae for the angular positions of the singular optical axes we now turn to the discussion of a real material and some novel effects regarding singular optical axes. For monoclinic
